 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003EThe Hippo Maintenance Manager is an intuitive web-based software providing a powerful demand and pm work order management tool, comprehensive reporting system and integrated Hippo Resource Library to ensure a timely and effective strategy that will increase the life cycle of your facility.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EHippo makes the integration process painless, less expensive, and less time-consuming. It lets property managers move past \u0026#8220;managing\u0026#8221; and get to the high-value work of optimizing their operations. By identifying opportunities, you are able to utilize your assets more effectively thus saving your organization money. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EHippo\u0026#8217;s broad functionality and multiple modules help to support small to large real estate portfolios, but without the high cost, complexity, and risks associated with custom-built systems. Hippo brings visibility, efficiency, intelligence, and control to real estate operations and processes in one integrated web-based application. Manage finances building-by-building in a consistent manner across your entire portfolio. Utilize tight integration with financial information and track aggregate costs more effectively. Benchmark a single building against other assets and use this information to negotiate better contracts. \u003C/p\u003E",
